{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_09_01_short",
  "title": "神崎莉央 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――東京シーサイド　タイアップ依頼を引き受けた後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、打ち合わせは終わったのに\n莉央さんにだけ残ってもらって",
      "startTime": 5.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "いいのよ。それで私に話しておきたいことって何？\n……やっぱり、東京シーサイドのCM撮影の件？",
      "startTime": 13.1999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。リーダーの莉央さんとは話しておきたいと思って\n今回、俺も橋本さんも同行出来なくて、迷惑をかけます",
      "startTime": 21.3999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が気に病むことはないわ。星見プロは忙しいもの\n貴方のいない現場にも、慣れなきゃいけないわ",
      "startTime": 31.166666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当にすみません。マネージャーを増やさないとですね",
      "startTime": 33.9889107189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで。それに、どんなにいい人がいても\n貴方のかわりにはならないわ",
      "startTime": 42.9999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それって、どういう意味ですか？",
      "startTime": 45.249456354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……ええと、貴方みたいな世話好きで\nおせっかいな人なんて、他にいないって意味よ！",
      "startTime": 51.9666682561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "だから勘違いはしないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 55.4350342235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……すみません……？",
      "startTime": 57.6428560537,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}